data.description: This charming two-story home is the perfect family retreat. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, it offers a warm and inviting atmosphere from the moment you step through the front door. The main level features an open-concept living area with a spacious living room and kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, and an island, perfect for entertaining. Downstairs you'll also find a bedroom, dining area, laundry room, and mud room area near the garage. Upstairs, the master suite is complete with a private en-suite bathroom and a his/her closet. Two additional bedrooms and an office space or 5th bedroom option, as well as a full bathroom are also located on the second floor, providing ample space for family members or guests. This fantastic home is close to Boiling Springs and Shelby as well as schools, parks, and shopping. Don't miss the chance to make this lovely two-story retreat your own.
